    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individuae Trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/79">Hugo</persName> et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/72">Lotharius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">reges</rs>. Conditio ad imaginem et similitudinem
                        suam primo homini creator omnium Deus coniugem adhibere voluit, ut, quia
                        angelicum ordinem de celis propter superbiam eiectum solus Adam supplere
                        nequiverat, cum Eva sibi adlata coniuge filios filiasque gignendo in
                        infinitum multiplicata prole decimum ordinem restauraret et viro mulier
                        iuvamen existeret, quam non ut virum simpliciter de limo terrae nasci
                        voluit, sed [ea]m de viri costa somno adempta producens in similem edidit
                        formam, ut una videlicet eademque caro ambobus esset, et de osse mulier
                        licet fragilem vigorem acciperet. Unde et scriptum est: derelinquat homo
                        patrem et matrem et adherebit uxori suae et erunt duo in carne una. Ipse
                        etiam mediator Dei et hominum novus homo adveniens in Chana Galileae nuptiis
                        interesse easque sanctificare voluit, sponsamque sibi sanctam Ecclesiam
                        socians posteris exemplum reliquit, ut nuptialis foederis colexio fieri non
                        desinat, et ad procreandam postmodum sobolem mutua indissolubilique
                        dilectione persistat. His itaque aliisque informatus exemplis, ego in
                        Christi nomine Lotharius divina favente clementia rex, divina dispensante
                        providentia consultuque nostrorum fidelium <persName ref="#people/1301"
                            >Adeleidem</persName> filiam divae memoriae <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/37">Rodulfi</persName> regis mihi in
                        coniugium copulare decernens, sponsare disposui. Quapropter omnium fidelium
                        sanctae Dei Ecclesiae nostrorumque presentium ac futurorum industria
                        noverit, qualiter prefatae Adeleide sponsae meae qu[asdam] <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >cortes</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fiscal_property">iuris nostri</rs>, videlicet <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >cortem</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Dowry #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/209">Marinco</geogName> et <rs key="#Curtes">cortem</rs>
                        de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Dowry #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/326">Coriano</geogName>, <rs key="#Curtes">cortem</rs>
                        quoque de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Dowry #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/139">Olonna</geogName> cum omnibus eorum pertinentiis, ad
                        quas <rs key="#Mansi">mille mansi</rs> pertinere cernuntur, in <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/2034">Cornini</geogName> etiam <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <rs key="#Curtes">cortem</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Dowry #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/239">Valli</geogName> cum <rs key="#Mansi">mansis
                            quin[qua]ginta</rs> et aliam <rs key="#Curtes">cortem</rs> in eodem
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Dowry #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/2333">Cornino</geogName> cum <rs key="#Mansi">mansis
                            triginta</rs>, <rs key="#Monasteries">abbatiam</rs> etiam de <orgName
                            key="#Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Dowry #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/130">Sexto</orgName> in <rs key="#Comitatus"
                            >comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/210">Lucensi</geogName> sitam cum
                            <rs key="#Mansi">mansis duo milia</rs>, et <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >abbatiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Dowry #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/131">Sancti Antimi</orgName> in <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/175">Sensensi</geogName> cum <rs
                            key="#Mansi">mansis mille</rs>, atque <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >abbatiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Dowry #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/301">domini Salvatoris</orgName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/737">in monte Amiate</placeName> coniacentem in <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/174">Clusensi</geogName> cum <rs
                            key="#Mansi">mansis quingentis</rs>, qui sunt in summa <rs key="#Mansi"
                            >mansi quattuor milia quingenti octoaginta</rs>, per hanc <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Dowry">nostri precepti paginam sub
                            dotis nomine concedimus</rs>, donamus poenitusque largimur, et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >de nostro iure et dominio in eius ius et dominium</rs> omnino
                        transfundimus et delegamus una cum castellis, casis, servis et ancillis,
                        aldionibus et aldiis, terris, campis, vineis, pratis, silvis, montibus,
                        vallibus, planitiebus, aquis aquarumque decursibus, molendinis,
                        piscationibus omnibusque rebus ad prelibatas cortes et abbatias in integrum
                        pertinentibus, quatenus proprietario iure habeat, teneat firmiterque
                        possideat, habeatque potestatem donandi, vendendi, commutandi, alienandi,
                        pro anima iudicandi et quicquid eius decreverit animus faciendi, omnium
                        hominum contradictione remota. Si quis igitur hoc nostrae dotis preceptum
                        infringere temptaverit, noverit se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri
                            optimi libras mille</rs>
                        <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">prefatae <persName
                                ref="#people/1301">Adeleidae</persName> puellae nostrisque et suis
                            heredibus</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur diligentiusque ab omnibus
                        observetur, manibus propriis roborantes anuli nostri inpressione subter
                        iussimus insigniri. Signa serenissorum (MF) (MF) domni Hugonis et Lotharii
                        regum. <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Gisbrandus"
                            >Giseprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1530">Azzonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. (SR) (SI D). Data pridie
                        idus decembris, anno dominicae incarnationis DCCCCXXXVIII, regni vero domni
                        Hugonis XII, filii eius Lotharii item regis VII, indictione XI. Actum in
                        Burgundia, in corte que <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2332"
                            >Columbaris</geogName> dicitur. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
